title: The.Independents.After.Show.2014.07.21.WS.WEB-DL.x264.XAiO
description:
WARNING: THIS VIDEO IS A MESS. The Fox Player really crapped the bed on this one. It kept going out of sync. Garbled video, etc. It's watchable. During the majority of it the sound is on & video is fine.

This is basically 480p widescreen. Recorded with Replay Video Catcher from FoxBusiness.com. Converted with AviDemux using Mpeg4 AVC (x264) & AAC (Faac). Downsized to 720x404, then cropped. Hence the oblong resolution. The black bars on the sides that come and go are due to the web player I rip these from.  I have nothing to do with the scene.
